Version numbering convention and mapping with Redmine tracker types.

first.second.third

first) when the interface change
second) internal changes or new features without interface change (Redmine tracker: "feature", "story/task" 
third) bug fixing (Redmine tracker: "bug")

Redmine tracker: "task" -> it depends by the changes in the code (on interface). e.g. refactoring is tracked as "task".
